Coolest Hack of the Season
Ice cubes + skincare = underrated summer magic🧊

Ice cubes can:
 • Shrink pores ✨
 • Calm acne 🌿
 • Reduce puffiness 👀
 • Add instant glow 💧

Here’s your DIY glow kit:
 • Green tea → fights breakouts 🍵
 • Cucumber juice → cools & hydrates 🥒
 • Aloe vera → soothes sunburn 🌞
 • Rose water → tones + brightens 🌹

Wrap in a soft cloth, glide over clean skin for 30–60 seconds. That’s it. Easy, natural, effective.
